"move curser on display lines not actual lines
nnoremap j gj
nnoremap k gk

"map keys to move lines
noremap <C-j> :m+<cr>==
noremap <C-k> :m-2<cr>==
inoremap <C-j> <Esc>:m+<cr>==gi
inoremap <C-k> <Esc>:m-2<cr>==gi
vnoremap <C-j> :m'>+<CR>gv=gv
